java -cp "c:\Program Files\[classpath]\startup.jar"
org.eclipse.core.launcher.Main -product com...

like to be able to start the application using UNC path, but when I try it fails
to launch.

-product com...

I am running on windows XP Professional system, Eclipse 3.0
Eclipse Version: 3.0.0
